*.ogg binary
*.aiff binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.fbx binary
*.obj binary
*.blend binary
*.mb binary
*.ma binary
*.max binary
*.dds binary
*.dll binary
*.dylib binary
*.so binary
*.exe binary
